Package: backup-manager-pro
Version: 1.0.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Desmond Clay <desmond@example.com>
Installed-Size: 48
Depends: python3:any, python3-tk, timeshift
Recommends: google-drive-ocamlfuse
Suggests: rclone
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/DarrylClay2005/backup-manager-pro
Description: Modern backup management system with GUI
 Backup Manager Pro is a comprehensive backup management system with a modern
 graphical interface designed for Linux systems. It provides automated system
 backups using Timeshift, local backup storage, and optional Google Drive
 integration.
 .
 Features:
  - Modern GUI interface built with Python Tkinter
  - Multiple backup types: Timeshift snapshots, local backups, cloud storage
  - Real-time monitoring with live status updates and activity logging
  - Configurable settings: backup paths, size limits, and scheduling
  - Smart storage management with automatic cleanup of old backups
  - Cross-platform compatibility across major Linux distributions
  - Desktop integration with system tray support
